@startuml

'-------------------------------
'----- Drive Controller --------

[Drive Controller] as DC

note top of DC
  Purpose:
    Control the state of the robot drive system. 
end note


'----------------------------------
'----- Remote Access Gateway ------

[Remote Access Gateway] as TG

note top of TG
  Purpose:
    Access point for remote client(s)
end note


'--------------------------------
'----- External Data Parser -----  

[] as EIMT

note top of EIMT
  Purpose:
    Translate messages from remote client(s)
    to internal messages
end note

'-----------------------------------------------
'----- Internal Message Broker Definition ------

[Internal Message Broker] as IMB

note top of IMB
  Purpose:
    Intermediary between internal 
    message producers and consumers
end note

'----------------------------------------------
'----- External Message Broker Definition -----

[External Message Broker] as EMB

note top of EMB
 Purpose:
   Intermediary between external 
   message producers and consumers
end note



@enduml
